OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FFor more than a year Derek and Shiv
OL,7,Fhave given up their own time to make
OL,8,Fthis project possible, and it has all
OL,9,Fbeen skilfully edited by ITV
OL,10,FMeridian's James Tee, who volunteered
OL,11,Fto take on the enormous task.
OL,13,FThe living link to D-Day and the
OL,14,FNormandy Landings is fast
OL,15,Fdisappearing. To be a veteran, you
OL,16,Fhave to be at least in your late 90s.
OL,17,FAnd many are now too frail to receive
OL,18,Fvisitors or speak at length or at all
OL,19,Fabout their experiences.
