OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FDerek and Shiv knew that they were the
OL,7,Famong the last ones who could record
OL,8,Fthe memories of those who fought in
OL,9,FWorld War Two, and set out to find
OL,10,Fwhat they thought would be a handful
OL,11,Fof veterans.
OL,13,FThey were wrong about that. In the
OL,14,Fyear from June 2023, they tracked down
OL,15,Fveteran after veteran, and not just
OL,16,Fthe ones on the front lines.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/11
