OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FDerek and Shiv visited care homes,
OL,7,Ftheir own homes, museums, regimental
OL,8,Fclubs, military shows and even an
OL,9,Faircraft hangar. In the process, they
OL,10,Ftalked to some extraordinary people.
OL,12,FITV Meridian asked one veteran, Marie
OL,13,FScott, to take us around the tunnels
OL,14,Fshe worked in during the war, and she
OL,15,Fsaid yes.
OL,17,FIt meant, for the first time in
OL,18,FMeridian's history, , from where the D-
OL,19,FDay operation was coordinated.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/11
