OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThe history there captured along with
OL,7,FMarie's memories and experiences, and
OL,8,Fit was only the second time she had
OL,9,Fgone back since the war herself.
OL,11,FMarie was one of the many veterans
OL,12,Fwith whom Derek and Shiv built a
OL,13,Fconnection during the project, their
OL,14,Fpassion making it all possible.
