OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FShiv and Derek haven't stopped
OL,7,Fthroughout this project and never said
OL,8,Fno to any veteran they found.JIn the
OL,9,Fend, they weren't able to keep every
OL,10,Fsingle word from every single veteran.
OL,11,FSome people understandably did not
OL,12,Ftell their stories from start to
OL,13,Ffinish, diverted and digressed and
OL,14,Ffocused on some episodes rather than
OL,15,Fothers.
OL,17,FSo they have been edited down and they
OL,18,Feach run from a few minutes to more
OL,19,Fthan half an hour. The only voices you
OL,20,Fhear are those of the veterans.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/11
