OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThey are available on a dedicated ITV
OL,7,Fwebsite, where they will remain long
OL,8,Fafter that living link disappears.
OL,10,FIt's not military history. Not a story
OL,11,Fabout ranks and regiments, tactics,
OL,12,Fstrategy and weaponry.
OL,14,FIt's the testimony of people who lived
OL,15,Fthrough extraordinary times, did their
OL,16,Fduty, and somehow came out the other
OL,17,Fside.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/11
