OL,6,FSoon along with museums, artefacts and
OL,7,Fhistoric sites, the stories collected
OL,8,Fby Derek and Shiv will be all that we
OL,9,Fhave left, but their efforts mean
OL,10,Fthey'll never be forgotten.
